ubjects and objects}} in accordance with [Assignment: organization-defined security policies].The organization provides a consistent interpretation of security attributes transmitted between distributed information system components.The information system implements [Assignment: organization-defined techniques or technologies] with [Assignment: organization-defined level of assurance] in associating security attributes to information.The organization ensures that security attributes associated with information are reassigned only via re-grading mechanisms validated using [Assignment: organization-defined techniques or procedures].The information system provides authorized individuals the capability to define or change the type and value of security attributes available for association with subjects and objects.' WHERE [Requirement_Id] = 10775
